dct_description_sm: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. North Decimal Degree 38.025000. South Decimal Degree 37.950000. East Decimal Degree 23.766667. West Decimal Degree 23.716667. Alternate title: Greece. Grid Prvisional. Index and inset map of the northern suburbs (1:20,000). Legend in English and Greek. Map shows public buildings and barracks occupied by Germans and Axis establishments according to 1943.
